Dear Colleagues,

recall that the

             International Category Theory Conference CT2015

will take place in Aveiro, Portugal, from Sunday, June 14 till Friday,
June 19.

We have now a conference website located at

 	ct2015.web.ua.pt.

It is also my pleasure to announce the

INVITED SPEAKERS
Clemens Berger - Universit?? de Nice
Julie Bergner - University of California, Riverside
Gabriella B??hm - Wigner Research Centre for Physics, Budapest
Richard Garner - Macquarie University, Sydney
Henning Krause - Bielefeld University
Diana Rodelo - University of Algarve

as selected by the Scientific Committee.

IMPORTANT DATES:
Abstract Submission: 27 of March
Acceptance: 25 of April
Early registration: 1 of May

A further announcement with information about accommodation,
registration and abstract submission will follow soon (probably in January).

PLEASE TAKE NOTE:

Directly preceding CT2015 there will be the 2015 AMS-EMS-SPM
International Meeting of the American Mathematical Society, the European
Mathematical Society and the hosting Portuguese Mathematical Society

http://aep-math2015.spm.pt,

which will take place in Porto (some 50 km from Aveiro) from Wednesday,
June 10, to Saturday, June 13. At this meeting, Gon??alo Gutierres and I
are organising a special session on "Categorical Methods in Algebra and
Topology" which will be held on Friday and Saturday (12/13 June) at the
Mathematics Department of the Faculty of Sciences of the University of
Porto. If you are interested in participating in this special session,
please contact me (dirk@ua.pt) or Gon??alo (ggutc@mat.uc.pt). For a
schedule of all special sessions see

    http://aep-math2015.spm.pt/ListOfSessions.

I hope to see you in Portugal next June!

Best regards
Dirk (for the organising committee)


